  ],
  "remarks": "Igor Zyuzin is a Russian businessperson, with business interests in the iron ore and steel, coal and energy sectors. Igor Zyuzin is a major shareholder and Chairman of the Board of Directors of Mechel PAO, a major Russian mining and metals company engaging in up-stream and down-stream activities within the Russian mining, metals and energy sectors. In particular, Mechel PAO is one of the leading Russian coal export companies. Those economic sectors provide a substantial source of revenue to the Government of the Russian Federation.",
